WEBVTT

00:11.040 --> 00:16.059
[Chunxiao Theater]

00:29.690 --> 00:32.130
[Nanxi Tribe, 15 years ago]

00:40.110 --> 00:41.030
Wait for me!

00:41.560 --> 00:42.280
Hurry up!

00:57.560 --> 00:58.550
It's the village!

00:58.550 --> 00:59.030
Brother!

00:59.030 --> 00:59.890
What happened?

01:02.390 --> 01:02.960
Brother!

01:03.950 --> 01:05.230
Someone's here! Hide!

01:21.000 --> 01:21.590
Father.

01:23.710 --> 01:24.310
Mother.

01:24.590 --> 01:25.150
Father.

01:26.590 --> 01:27.230
Mother!

01:27.680 --> 01:28.710
Father!

01:29.430 --> 01:31.000
-Mother!
-Mother!

01:31.280 --> 01:33.310
Mother, where are you?

01:33.680 --> 01:35.680
Mother! Father!

01:35.710 --> 01:36.560
Brother,

01:37.000 --> 01:38.600
where are Father and Mother?

01:41.710 --> 01:42.680
Mother!

01:42.710 --> 01:43.789
They are all dead.

01:45.560 --> 01:46.200
Father!

01:46.789 --> 01:48.270
Father, where are you?

01:52.400 --> 01:55.240
[Young Zhan Ziming]

01:52.780 --> 01:53.910
Brother, you eat it.

01:56.720 --> 02:00.590
[Young Zhan Ziyu]

01:57.870 --> 01:59.509
I'm not hungry. You eat it.

03:20.490 --> 03:25.690
[REBIRTH]

03:26.070 --> 03:28.690
[Episode 13]

03:32.910 --> 03:34.430
No need for formalities, Director Zhang.

03:34.430 --> 03:35.090
Take a seat.

03:35.340 --> 03:36.190
I dare not.

03:38.079 --> 03:38.750
Sit.

03:40.060 --> 03:40.620
Yes.

03:48.150 --> 03:48.870
And this is?

03:48.870 --> 03:50.250
You don't need to ask, Director Zhang.

03:50.250 --> 03:51.050
I understand.

03:51.360 --> 03:53.020
My late-night visit this time

03:53.540 --> 03:55.070
is somewhat presumptuous.

03:55.280 --> 03:56.240
Not at all.

03:56.800 --> 03:59.310
Your Highness, may I ask why

04:00.030 --> 04:01.960
you're visiting at this time?

04:12.760 --> 04:15.380
I've long heard you compiled a book

04:15.750 --> 04:17.480
named Compendium of Creation.

04:17.510 --> 04:20.000
It consists of five volumes:
Metal, Wood, Water, Fire, and Earth.

04:20.000 --> 04:20.480
Metal

04:21.070 --> 04:22.040
is metallurgy.

04:22.270 --> 04:22.750
Wood

04:22.920 --> 04:24.920
is formations and fortifications.

04:25.000 --> 04:27.510
Water covers meteorology
and water conservancy.

04:27.510 --> 04:28.040
Earth

04:28.420 --> 04:29.390
is topography.

04:29.800 --> 04:33.000
It is a grand and invaluable work,

04:33.180 --> 04:34.600
a classified archive of Biantang

04:34.600 --> 04:36.190
kept within the Manufacturing Bureau.

04:36.190 --> 04:37.310
I've come today

04:37.480 --> 04:39.270
to borrow it.

04:39.920 --> 04:42.360
Will you do me this favor?

04:46.720 --> 04:48.270
Your Highness, you are the ruler

04:48.270 --> 04:49.520
and I am your subject.

04:49.560 --> 04:51.270
This compendium I compiled

04:51.390 --> 04:52.950
belongs to Biantang.

04:53.250 --> 04:54.360
If you wish to use it,

04:54.360 --> 04:56.350
I will certainly help.

04:57.960 --> 04:58.750
However,

04:59.000 --> 05:01.480
it falls under the Manufacturing Bureau,

05:01.560 --> 05:03.680
a highly confidential office.

05:03.830 --> 05:06.270
You would need an imperial decree
from His Majesty,

05:06.270 --> 05:08.350
and with that I will certainly help.

05:17.390 --> 05:19.680
Lord Zhang, you've served
as an official for years,

05:19.680 --> 05:22.800
so you are naturally no stranger
to the affairs of the imperial court.

05:22.800 --> 05:23.930
You should know that

05:24.250 --> 05:26.720
some matters are appropriate
for requesting a decree,

05:26.720 --> 05:29.560
and some are not.

05:30.190 --> 05:31.720
Since I am the Crown Prince,

05:31.800 --> 05:33.830
I'm the future ruler of Biantang.

05:34.310 --> 05:37.000
Helping me would not be considered
overstepping.

05:37.000 --> 05:39.720
And I will certainly
reward you handsomely.

05:40.060 --> 05:40.920
What do you say?

05:47.140 --> 05:48.740
I-If that's the case, Your Highness,

05:48.740 --> 05:50.620
I understand.

05:50.750 --> 05:52.409
But I have one question to ask.

05:52.630 --> 05:54.240
If you answer truthfully,

05:54.240 --> 05:55.830
I will certainly help.

05:55.830 --> 05:56.800
Feel free to ask.

05:59.070 --> 06:01.920
Your Highness, what do you intend to use

06:03.190 --> 06:04.990
the Compendium of Creation for?

06:11.310 --> 06:12.120
I...

06:14.150 --> 06:18.150
I need... the Metal volume.

06:18.510 --> 06:19.360
Your Highness,

06:19.360 --> 06:21.560
since Lord Zhang has his difficulties,

06:21.800 --> 06:23.560
we shouldn't force him.

06:24.480 --> 06:25.340
Why don't we...

06:26.070 --> 06:27.130
take our leave now?

06:29.340 --> 06:31.190
Alright. Alright.

06:32.800 --> 06:33.330
Let's go.

06:33.560 --> 06:34.240
Farewell,

06:34.750 --> 06:35.800
Your Highness.

06:57.950 --> 06:59.880
This person is not Director Zhang.

07:06.750 --> 07:08.210
We fell into Mother's trap.

07:08.210 --> 07:09.240
What do we do now?

07:09.360 --> 07:10.290
How do we get out?

07:16.430 --> 07:17.270
Cover up.

07:17.750 --> 07:18.680
Why?

07:18.680 --> 07:20.140
Cover up your face with it.

07:22.190 --> 07:22.950
What's the point of this?

07:22.950 --> 07:23.600
Be quiet.

07:23.920 --> 07:25.320
Just follow me from here.

07:40.530 --> 07:41.090
Let's go.

07:42.610 --> 07:43.220
Stop!

07:44.110 --> 07:44.960
Catch them!

07:47.560 --> 07:48.270
Stop!

07:53.490 --> 07:54.600
I want them alive!

07:54.600 --> 07:55.730
Arrest them!

07:55.750 --> 07:56.360
Yes!

07:56.360 --> 07:57.190
Can you slow down?

07:57.190 --> 07:58.050
I can't keep up.

07:58.070 --> 07:59.040
If you say one more word,

07:59.040 --> 07:59.850
you're on your own!

07:59.850 --> 08:00.480
I don't know martial arts!

08:00.480 --> 08:01.000
Stop!

08:03.120 --> 08:03.780
Over there!

08:04.160 --> 08:04.800
This way!

08:04.800 --> 08:05.660
Hurry up! Stop!

08:05.680 --> 08:06.310
Stop!

08:15.820 --> 08:16.820
-Stop!
-Let's go!

08:18.950 --> 08:19.600
Stop!

08:20.630 --> 08:21.190
After them!

08:21.190 --> 08:22.800
Wait! I'm exhausted!

08:23.920 --> 08:24.560
This way!

08:25.600 --> 08:26.270
Zhuge Yue,

08:26.360 --> 08:27.920
I'm just a frail scholar.

08:28.120 --> 08:29.900
Do you have to be so inhumane?

08:30.290 --> 08:31.800
I haven't seen any literary talent
from you.

08:31.800 --> 08:33.409
How dare you call yourself a scholar?

08:33.409 --> 08:34.049
You...

08:39.720 --> 08:40.360
Qiao?

08:41.260 --> 08:42.020
Come with me.

08:44.510 --> 08:45.360
Stay close.

08:47.750 --> 08:48.440
Qiao,

08:48.440 --> 08:49.390
why are you here?

08:50.360 --> 08:52.440
I guessed you'd fall into
the Empress's trap.

08:52.440 --> 08:54.170
I had Wang Shi'er bring me here.

08:56.270 --> 08:56.930
We're here.

09:02.480 --> 09:05.000
This leads outside
the Manufacturing Bureau.

09:05.000 --> 09:06.200
We'll go out from here.

09:06.200 --> 09:08.270
Wang Shi'er is waiting for us outside.

09:08.270 --> 09:08.840
Follow me.

09:08.840 --> 09:09.700
It's so deep...

09:12.910 --> 09:13.480
Zhuge...

09:15.770 --> 09:17.370
Li Ce, hurry up and come down.

09:17.670 --> 09:19.360
Don't be afraid. I'll catch you.

09:19.360 --> 09:20.320
I-I...

09:21.550 --> 09:22.750
I'm not afraid, Qiao.

09:23.320 --> 09:24.380
Catch me, will you?

09:24.630 --> 09:25.490
I'll catch you!

09:25.790 --> 09:26.590
Come down now!

09:33.270 --> 09:34.810
Why did you, a grown man, catch me?

09:34.810 --> 09:36.810
I told you I didn't need to be caught.

09:41.240 --> 09:41.970
Zhuge Yue...

09:44.810 --> 09:45.470
You...

09:47.630 --> 09:48.480
Wait for me!

09:54.720 --> 09:55.360
Qiao,

09:55.750 --> 09:56.670
where are we?

09:57.080 --> 09:59.410
This canal used to be for flood discharge.

09:59.480 --> 10:00.670
It's abandoned now.

10:01.030 --> 10:03.440
Keep walking, and we'll reach
Tianyuan Bridge in Rong District.

10:03.440 --> 10:04.640
Wang Shi'er found it.

10:11.240 --> 10:12.240
You guys go first.

10:12.600 --> 10:14.800
I'll meet you at Tianyuan Bridge later.

10:17.150 --> 10:17.720
Hurry!

10:32.220 --> 10:33.280
Search over there!

10:37.790 --> 10:39.240
Go! Search over there!

10:39.480 --> 10:40.960
Search every spot!

10:41.460 --> 10:43.230
Don't let those two get away!

10:55.080 --> 10:57.570
It is a grand and invaluable work,

10:58.440 --> 11:00.300
a classified archive of Biantang

11:00.870 --> 11:03.070
kept within the Manufacturing Bureau.

11:03.870 --> 11:05.120
"Tianji" means...

11:05.790 --> 11:06.790
Tianji Pavilion.

11:10.600 --> 11:12.660
"The river originates from Kunlun."

11:13.320 --> 11:14.590
[Tianji Pavilion]

12:00.790 --> 12:02.440
Who's there? Who's in there?

12:05.840 --> 12:06.390
Search!

12:15.550 --> 12:17.150
Did you find what you wanted?

12:17.670 --> 12:18.200
Here.

12:32.490 --> 12:33.090
Xing.

12:36.910 --> 12:38.040
Let's talk outside.

12:50.120 --> 12:50.720
Li Ce.

12:50.840 --> 12:51.510
Qiao,

12:51.600 --> 12:52.270
are you alright?

12:52.270 --> 12:53.000
Where did you go?

12:53.000 --> 12:53.790
There have been several waves of troops

12:53.790 --> 12:54.920
searching the area.

12:55.150 --> 12:56.630
Let's find a place to hide first.

12:56.630 --> 12:57.840
There's a hiding spot up ahead.

12:57.840 --> 12:58.870
I'll take you there.

12:58.870 --> 12:59.480
Okay.

12:59.910 --> 13:00.840
-Let's go.
-Let's go.

13:00.840 --> 13:01.550
Once we get there,

13:01.550 --> 13:02.440
I'll draw the pursuers away,

13:02.440 --> 13:04.770
and you wait for an opportunity to escape.

13:53.310 --> 13:53.910
Qiao,

13:54.030 --> 13:54.910
I'm injured.

13:55.150 --> 13:55.750
Look.

13:57.030 --> 13:57.720
Injured?

13:58.000 --> 13:59.550
It's just a scrape.

13:59.550 --> 14:00.440
No.

14:00.600 --> 14:01.720
It hurts a lot.

14:02.070 --> 14:03.000
Look carefully.

14:03.030 --> 14:04.020
What's going on?

14:05.360 --> 14:06.120
Let me see.

14:06.120 --> 14:07.000
Look closely.

14:09.510 --> 14:10.910
Why does it hurt so much?

14:11.760 --> 14:13.760
I feel dizzy, my vision is blurry,

14:13.790 --> 14:16.120
my legs are weak,
and my hands are shaking.

14:16.360 --> 14:17.620
I think I have internal injuries.

14:17.620 --> 14:19.030
Oh, no.

14:19.030 --> 14:21.000
I can't even stand anymore.

14:21.440 --> 14:22.270
I can't stand.

14:25.480 --> 14:26.410
Feeling better?

14:26.600 --> 14:28.270
It's getting worse.

14:29.120 --> 14:30.980
Let me lean on you a little longer.

14:40.080 --> 14:40.720
Qiao,

14:40.910 --> 14:42.170
where did Zhuge Yue go?

15:29.750 --> 15:31.270
Are you saying that the Crown Prince
was wearing a veil

15:31.270 --> 15:32.430
when he fled,

15:32.840 --> 15:34.560
and none of you saw his face?

15:35.270 --> 15:36.720
It was too dark at the time.

15:36.720 --> 15:38.720
We could only judge from his figure.

15:38.790 --> 15:41.000
It should have been His Highness.

15:41.360 --> 15:42.910
Not only did you fail to catch him,

15:42.910 --> 15:44.650
but you also didn't see his face clearly.

15:44.650 --> 15:46.310
What's the use of keeping you?

15:47.030 --> 15:47.670
Guards!

15:52.030 --> 15:52.870
Drag them out.

15:53.910 --> 15:54.670
Kill them.

15:55.200 --> 15:56.200
Spare us, Your Majesty!

15:56.200 --> 15:58.000
Your Majesty, have mercy!

15:58.550 --> 15:59.670
Spare us!

16:00.510 --> 16:02.640
Your Majesty! Your Majesty, spare us!

16:02.960 --> 16:03.550
Spare us!

16:03.550 --> 16:04.750
Please calm your anger, Your Majesty!

16:04.750 --> 16:06.880
Please calm your anger, Your Majesty!

16:06.910 --> 16:08.440
Please calm your anger, Your Majesty!

16:08.440 --> 16:10.120
Get out! Get out, all of you!

16:10.670 --> 16:11.320
Get out!

16:20.270 --> 16:21.070
Your Majesty.

16:21.750 --> 16:22.750
I failed you.

16:23.750 --> 16:27.240
If you're really too angry, punish me.

16:38.870 --> 16:40.270
What's the use of beating you to death?

16:40.270 --> 16:42.200
Will that get me the evidence
that the Crown Prince colluded

16:42.200 --> 16:43.910
with a foreign power
and stole the archives?

16:43.910 --> 16:45.710
Your life isn't worth that much!

16:47.200 --> 16:48.750
My life is worth nothing,

16:49.200 --> 16:50.750
but it belongs to you.

16:52.910 --> 16:55.550
What I need is to get rid of him.

16:55.870 --> 16:57.150
If you can't do that,

16:57.240 --> 16:58.790
you're useless to me!

16:59.270 --> 17:00.150
I can testify!

17:00.960 --> 17:02.630
I did see the Crown Prince.

17:03.270 --> 17:05.550
It was him who broke into
the Manufacturing Bureau at night.

17:05.550 --> 17:06.880
You can testify?

17:09.680 --> 17:11.010
Who do you think you are?

17:11.349 --> 17:12.310
Without me,

17:12.640 --> 17:14.750
would His Majesty
listen to a word you say?

17:14.750 --> 17:15.829
Who do you think you are

17:15.829 --> 17:17.920
to accuse the Crown Prince of Biantang?

17:17.920 --> 17:19.030
I'm telling you,

17:19.480 --> 17:21.640
you didn't bring back any witnesses
or material evidence today.

17:21.640 --> 17:23.960
Even if your subordinates swear

17:23.960 --> 17:25.920
that the Crown Prince broke into
the Manufacturing Bureau at night,

17:25.920 --> 17:27.579
His Majesty won't believe it.

17:27.829 --> 17:29.720
He will only turn a blind eye

17:29.720 --> 17:30.680
and brush me off.

17:31.550 --> 17:32.680
For him,

17:33.000 --> 17:35.310
bloodline and the throne
are the most important.

17:35.310 --> 17:38.200
I am just a woman.

17:43.440 --> 17:44.240
Your Majesty.

17:45.510 --> 17:46.720
We haven't lost.

17:47.350 --> 17:48.680
We still have Ziming.

17:51.030 --> 17:52.920
And the child in her womb.

18:00.200 --> 18:02.200
Greetings, Your Majesty.

18:02.240 --> 18:04.240
May Your Majesty enjoy good health.

18:07.510 --> 18:08.550
Look up.

18:17.000 --> 18:19.260
Are you really pregnant with Ce's child?

18:20.880 --> 18:22.940
I dare not deceive you, Your Majesty.

18:23.270 --> 18:25.270
It is indeed the Crown Prince's kid.

18:25.790 --> 18:27.050
Since that's the case,

18:27.310 --> 18:28.940
you should move out
of the Crown Prince's Mansion.

18:28.940 --> 18:31.390
[Boque Palace]

18:29.550 --> 18:30.640
Yes.

18:38.030 --> 18:39.490
We uncovered everything.

18:39.750 --> 18:41.790
Lady Ziming's original surname was Zhan.

18:41.790 --> 18:43.830
She is Zhan Ziyu's biological sister,

18:43.830 --> 18:44.400
and also the Empress's

18:44.400 --> 18:45.640
deepest planted spy

18:45.640 --> 18:47.370
in the Crown Prince's Mansion.

18:47.480 --> 18:49.030
After her identity was exposed,

18:49.030 --> 18:50.270
she left on her own.

18:51.720 --> 18:53.380
I was born as the Crown Prince.

18:54.160 --> 18:57.110
Living in the palace, I've always known
danger is everywhere.

18:57.110 --> 19:00.310
I never dared to easily reveal
my true feelings to anyone.

19:00.920 --> 19:02.070
But Ziming…

19:04.160 --> 19:06.240
I thought she was different.

19:08.350 --> 19:09.550
Stop! Don't run!

19:10.310 --> 19:10.910
Stop!

19:16.560 --> 19:17.490
How dare you run!

19:17.880 --> 19:18.680
Keep running!

19:18.790 --> 19:19.510
Stop!

19:24.550 --> 19:26.060
Go back and tell your master

19:26.060 --> 19:26.970
that I bought

19:27.480 --> 19:28.140
this slave.

19:51.030 --> 19:51.590
Li Ce,

19:51.880 --> 19:52.880
I promised you

19:53.270 --> 19:54.550
that once we rescue He Xiao,

19:54.550 --> 19:55.920
I would regroup

19:56.200 --> 20:00.060
and help you reclaim your rightful power
as Crown Prince of Biantang.

20:06.880 --> 20:09.010
Burn all of Lady Ziming's belongings.

21:02.400 --> 21:03.260
Your Highness.

21:03.880 --> 21:05.350
These are battle reports
from various regions

21:05.350 --> 21:06.880
of Great Yong and Great Yan.

21:09.850 --> 21:13.050
It seems they are preparing
to exchange prisoners of war.

21:15.920 --> 21:17.520
There's nothing important.

21:25.790 --> 21:27.830
Since the Compendium of Creation
has been found,

21:27.830 --> 21:29.030
take some rest first.

21:29.440 --> 21:31.590
We will enter the palace today
to bid farewell

21:31.590 --> 21:33.390
and depart for Ximeng tomorrow.

21:50.790 --> 21:52.120
[Great Yong and Great Yan are set to
exchange prisoners of war in a border valley]

21:52.120 --> 21:53.450
[at the end of the month. There may be
further actions to follow.]

22:04.640 --> 22:05.720
Let's make a deal.

22:06.350 --> 22:07.480
I need 20 days.

22:08.350 --> 22:09.270
After 20 days,

22:10.460 --> 22:11.660
I will leave with you.

22:12.680 --> 22:14.480
Why should I make a deal with you?

22:16.030 --> 22:19.630
If you bring back the Compendium of Creation
with missing pages,

22:19.750 --> 22:22.010
do you think King Ximeng will let you off?

22:33.000 --> 22:33.880
Zhuge Yue.

22:35.000 --> 22:36.680
You think you're threatening me?

22:36.680 --> 22:37.920
Your poisoning relapsed yesterday

22:37.920 --> 22:40.030
because we have already passed
the agreed time.

22:40.030 --> 22:41.360
If you go another 10 days

22:42.070 --> 22:43.530
without the Blood on Snow,

22:43.960 --> 22:44.830
you will die.

22:45.110 --> 22:46.310
There are some things

22:47.330 --> 22:48.440
I must do.

22:56.110 --> 22:57.770
I'll give you one last chance.

22:59.030 --> 23:00.220
Give me the compendium

23:00.220 --> 23:01.820
and go back to Ximeng with me.

23:01.920 --> 23:02.830
You know

23:03.900 --> 23:05.010
you can't kill me.

23:09.110 --> 23:11.240
It's for that Chu Qiao again, isn't it?

23:18.440 --> 23:20.300
I want you to help me do two things.

23:22.400 --> 23:23.240
First,

23:24.400 --> 23:25.510
find out

23:25.830 --> 23:28.310
if there is a man named He Xiao
among the prisoners

23:28.310 --> 23:30.440
handed over to Great Yan by Great Yong.

23:30.440 --> 23:31.330
Second,

23:31.750 --> 23:32.550
if there is,

23:33.070 --> 23:34.510
I need 20 days

23:35.030 --> 23:36.030
to save this man.

23:36.270 --> 23:37.800
You don't have to go with me.

23:38.110 --> 23:39.160
Just stay in Tangjing

23:39.160 --> 23:40.680
and buy me some time.

23:43.400 --> 23:45.310
As long as you help me
complete these 2 things,

23:45.310 --> 23:47.790
I will also help you
accomplish the 2 things

23:48.990 --> 23:50.450
King Ximeng assigned you.

23:51.750 --> 23:52.680
Hurry up!

23:53.000 --> 23:54.270
Get in line!

23:57.680 --> 23:58.310
Keep up!

23:59.790 --> 24:00.400
Hurry!

24:01.750 --> 24:02.480
Keep up!

24:03.750 --> 24:04.950
What's all the noise?

24:08.510 --> 24:09.200
Elder.

24:10.110 --> 24:11.040
I have been ordered

24:11.040 --> 24:13.440
to dispatch an elite unit
to escort prisoners of war.

24:13.440 --> 24:14.640
We are pressed for time,

24:14.640 --> 24:15.680
I apologize

24:15.880 --> 24:17.070
for disturbing your rest.

24:17.070 --> 24:18.600
Making a fuss over nothing.

24:19.270 --> 24:21.880
They're just a few dying men.
Why do you need a whole unit for that?

24:21.880 --> 24:22.550
Yes.

24:22.880 --> 24:24.440
We've also been ordered
to assign 2 fast horses each

24:24.440 --> 24:26.170
and rush to the main camp first.

24:26.680 --> 24:29.270
We've been instructed
to reach Lincheng within 5 days.

24:29.270 --> 24:31.000
Reach Lincheng in 5 days?

24:31.680 --> 24:34.170
Are they trying to run the men and horses
to death?

24:34.170 --> 24:36.020
Who the hell gave this order?

24:36.590 --> 24:37.920
Mind your words, Elder.

24:38.030 --> 24:39.630
This is His Majesty's order.

24:41.550 --> 24:43.210
Then I'd like to ask him myself

24:43.280 --> 24:46.510
whether the lives
of our Lanchuan soldiers are worthless!

24:46.510 --> 24:47.510
Prepare my horse!

24:58.240 --> 24:59.040
Your Majesty,

24:59.550 --> 25:02.270
the scent of Platycladi seeds can
calm your mind and nourish your energy.

25:02.270 --> 25:04.030
It can also soothe your nerves.

25:07.590 --> 25:08.350
Your Majesty,

25:08.350 --> 25:09.540
Elder Lanchuan requests an audience.

25:09.540 --> 25:10.350
I won't see him.

25:10.350 --> 25:12.750
Your Majesty,
is it because you feel guilty

25:13.000 --> 25:14.330
that you dare not see me?

25:14.810 --> 25:16.670
Lincheng is far from the Capital.

25:16.790 --> 25:17.880
Why are we taking the risk of losing

25:17.880 --> 25:19.110
our elite soldiers and fine horses

25:19.110 --> 25:21.220
just to escort a few death-row prisoners
of Great Yong?

25:21.220 --> 25:23.700
Are the lives of Great Yan warriors

25:23.750 --> 25:25.550
worth less than a few dying men?

25:25.550 --> 25:27.280
Do I need to explain my thoughts

25:27.600 --> 25:29.880
to you one by one?

25:30.000 --> 25:31.680
Your Majesty, ever since your recovery,

25:31.680 --> 25:33.000
you've become like a different person.

25:33.000 --> 25:35.110
Not only do you want a truce
with Great Yong,

25:35.110 --> 25:36.680
but now you also want to exchange
prisoners of war with them.

25:36.680 --> 25:39.200
Everything you've done
goes against your previous nature.

25:39.200 --> 25:39.720
Do you think

25:39.720 --> 25:41.830
we elders are so blind

25:41.830 --> 25:43.720
that we can't see your intentions?

25:43.720 --> 25:44.680
You simply want to exchange

25:44.680 --> 25:47.160
for He Xiao, the Xiuli Army general,

25:47.160 --> 25:48.520
so you can lure a woman here.

25:48.520 --> 25:49.240
Cheng Yuan!

25:49.680 --> 25:52.590
Drag this outspoken Elder Lanchuan

25:52.880 --> 25:53.680
out of here.

25:55.310 --> 25:56.110
Your Majesty,

25:56.310 --> 25:58.110
General Cheng is no longer here.

25:58.750 --> 26:00.160
See Elder Lanchuan out.

26:00.160 --> 26:00.920
Guards!

26:04.350 --> 26:05.440
Who dares to touch me!

26:05.440 --> 26:06.270
No need for it!

26:06.710 --> 26:07.960
I will leave on my own!

26:12.820 --> 26:14.750
Your Majesty, you're in a bad mood.

26:14.750 --> 26:17.810
How about going for
a horseback ride with me to cheer up?

26:31.240 --> 26:32.100
You lost again.

26:32.430 --> 26:34.030
I just learned how to ride.

26:34.270 --> 26:36.200
Your Majesty, you're bullying me.

26:36.830 --> 26:38.160
Then I will let you win.

26:38.790 --> 26:39.350
Let's go!

26:45.830 --> 26:46.550
Stop.

26:47.550 --> 26:48.310
Turn around.

26:54.590 --> 26:55.280
Cheng Yuan?

26:56.210 --> 26:57.140
Why are you here?

26:57.200 --> 26:59.330
Your Majesty, you don't want to see me,

26:59.400 --> 27:00.480
so I will leave.

27:07.570 --> 27:08.720
I'm asking you!

27:09.640 --> 27:10.440
Your Majesty,

27:11.110 --> 27:12.950
I have joined the army
since I was a child.

27:12.950 --> 27:15.030
The military camp of Great Yan is my home.

27:15.030 --> 27:17.360
The Black Eagle Army and you
are my family.

27:17.830 --> 27:19.030
Great Yan is so large,

27:19.750 --> 27:21.550
but I don't know where to go.

27:33.000 --> 27:36.200
The racecourse is the closest place
to the military camp.

27:36.640 --> 27:38.160
I found a job here

27:39.360 --> 27:40.360
to make a living.

27:41.400 --> 27:43.680
I never thought I would meet you here.

27:44.720 --> 27:47.310
Your Majesty,
just pretend you didn't see me today.

27:47.310 --> 27:48.590
I will leave now...

27:49.510 --> 27:50.640
and never come back.

28:02.070 --> 28:02.750
Guards!

28:11.110 --> 28:13.040
Prepare a horse for General Cheng!

28:41.580 --> 28:42.210
My Lady,

28:42.270 --> 28:43.510
let me do it.

28:43.610 --> 28:45.810
Or just let the maids and servants do it.

28:46.030 --> 28:47.270
If you get too tired,

28:47.270 --> 28:49.000
the Prince of Luo will blame us.

28:49.250 --> 28:50.640
I stay here all day

28:50.790 --> 28:52.450
and have nothing to do anyway.

28:53.030 --> 28:55.290
I might as well help out with some chores.

29:00.550 --> 29:02.750
Miss, you look different
these past few days.

29:02.750 --> 29:03.750
How so?

29:04.160 --> 29:04.830
You smile more,

29:04.830 --> 29:06.590
and you've become more beautiful.

29:06.590 --> 29:07.590
But it makes sense.

29:07.590 --> 29:08.830
I've never seen His Highness

29:08.830 --> 29:10.690
care so much about anyone before.

29:21.560 --> 29:24.590
[Portrait of Zhao Chun'er,
Princess of Great Yong]

29:26.960 --> 29:27.720
Let me go!

29:29.830 --> 29:31.230
Chun'er, let me explain.

29:32.070 --> 29:33.640
You've known who I am for a long time.

29:33.640 --> 29:35.310
How long were you planning
to hide it from me?

29:35.310 --> 29:37.240
What's your real purpose in treating me
so well, always attending to me,

29:37.240 --> 29:38.510
and caring toward me?

29:39.110 --> 29:39.830
Chun'er!

29:40.070 --> 29:42.350
I got that portrait by chance
a few days ago.

29:42.350 --> 29:43.000
I didn't tell you

29:43.000 --> 29:43.680
because I knew

29:43.680 --> 29:45.290
you didn't want to talk about your past,

29:45.290 --> 29:47.420
and I didn't want to remind you of that.

29:47.480 --> 29:48.480
I didn't mean to hide it.

29:48.480 --> 29:49.350
Stop talking!

29:49.780 --> 29:51.510
I will never believe you again!

30:16.510 --> 30:17.770
Someone's robbing me!

30:18.000 --> 30:18.790
Help!

30:19.000 --> 30:19.960
Help!

30:20.440 --> 30:21.830
Someone is robbing me!

30:23.000 --> 30:23.880
Help!

30:24.680 --> 30:26.270
I was robbed!

30:27.860 --> 30:28.730
Help!

30:34.880 --> 30:36.160
In broad daylight,

30:36.160 --> 30:37.790
how dare you rob someone in the street!

30:37.790 --> 30:38.720
Get lost!

30:41.150 --> 30:41.780
Miss,

30:42.400 --> 30:44.330
this jade pendant is yours, right?

30:50.240 --> 30:52.330
This area is often frequented by merchants
from beyond the borders,

30:52.330 --> 30:54.030
and there's all kinds of people around.

30:54.030 --> 30:55.400
A young lady like you
should be more careful

30:55.400 --> 30:56.660
when you're out alone.

30:57.990 --> 30:58.640
Miss?

30:59.510 --> 31:00.570
Your jade pendant.

31:01.510 --> 31:02.870
What's wrong with you?

31:03.000 --> 31:05.000
You didn't even thank our Princess.

31:09.640 --> 31:10.270
Princess.

31:14.680 --> 31:15.440
This girl...

31:16.110 --> 31:17.840
looks a bit like someone I know.

31:19.370 --> 31:20.170
It's alright.

31:21.030 --> 31:21.880
Let's go.

31:22.350 --> 31:22.960
Yes.

31:31.000 --> 31:31.530
How is it?

31:31.920 --> 31:32.920
Is there any news?

31:34.200 --> 31:35.070
For the past half month,

31:35.070 --> 31:37.680
I've asked many friends to gather
information in Zhenhuangcheng,

31:37.680 --> 31:39.080
but there's been no news.

31:40.550 --> 31:41.410
What about you?

31:41.440 --> 31:42.110
Me too.

31:42.110 --> 31:43.270
I think it's very strange.

31:43.270 --> 31:44.680
When I was a wandering physician,

31:44.680 --> 31:45.960
I got to know quite a few people.

31:45.960 --> 31:47.480
Not just people from the martial world,

31:47.480 --> 31:49.310
but also nobles and aristocrats.

31:49.310 --> 31:50.350
But for some reason,

31:50.350 --> 31:51.550
none of them have heard of He Xiao

31:51.550 --> 31:52.720
in the prisoner of war camps
they've inquired about.

31:52.720 --> 31:55.350
He Xiao is now a prisoner of war
under Zhao Che's command.

31:55.350 --> 31:57.350
Zhao Che has always been strict
with his army.

31:57.350 --> 31:58.750
If you're not in his army,

31:58.790 --> 32:00.920
it's very hard to get any information.

32:04.030 --> 32:04.830
Who are you?

32:05.510 --> 32:06.510
What do you want?

32:08.200 --> 32:09.860
I'm here to see your princess.

32:14.350 --> 32:15.880
Great Yong and Great Yan
have agreed to exchange

32:15.880 --> 32:17.200
a batch of prisoners of war in Lincheng,

32:17.200 --> 32:18.880
which is near Baichuan, in ten days.

32:18.880 --> 32:20.310
I've already had people inquire about

32:20.310 --> 32:22.200
the list of these prisoners of war.

32:22.200 --> 32:23.480
He Xiao is indeed on it.

32:24.550 --> 32:26.340
Yan Xun has called a truce
with Great Yong for months,

32:26.340 --> 32:29.160
and he's been continuously sending
the Black Eagle Army to search for you.

32:29.160 --> 32:30.750
The real purpose

32:31.110 --> 32:33.570
of this prisoner exchange
should be He Xiao.

32:33.720 --> 32:35.450
Thank you for the information.

32:35.960 --> 32:37.160
How will you save him?

32:37.440 --> 32:39.440
How do you know I'm going to save him?

32:43.920 --> 32:46.640
You've been secretly training troops
in this restaurant for Li Ce,

32:46.640 --> 32:49.440
and you disguised yourself
as Princess Fu in Tangjing.

32:49.440 --> 32:50.470
Is it because you're fond of
the luxurious life

32:50.470 --> 32:51.720
in the Crown Prince's Mansion,

32:51.720 --> 32:55.520
or because you want to get involved
in Biantang's palace intrigues?

32:56.270 --> 32:57.670
Aren't you doing all this

32:57.750 --> 33:00.000
just so that when you finally get news
of He Xiao,

33:00.000 --> 33:01.060
you can go save him?

33:01.680 --> 33:02.310
Yes.

33:02.680 --> 33:03.680
You're right.

33:05.210 --> 33:06.660
But this is my business.

33:07.160 --> 33:08.760
It has nothing to do with you.

33:11.640 --> 33:12.770
Lincheng is at least

33:13.070 --> 33:14.720
15 days' journey from Tangjing.

33:14.720 --> 33:15.510
Even if you set off immediately,

33:15.510 --> 33:17.270
you won't make it in time before Great Yan

33:17.270 --> 33:17.960
takes He Xiao away.

33:17.960 --> 33:19.790
You can only
take the Biantang official road,

33:19.790 --> 33:22.000
switch to the waterway halfway,
and go through Qingluan Pass

33:22.000 --> 33:23.860
to arrive exactly within 10 days.

33:23.920 --> 33:26.200
But the official road
requires an imperial pass.

33:26.200 --> 33:26.880
How can I take it?

33:26.880 --> 33:28.830
Under the name of the Ximeng envoy team,

33:28.830 --> 33:30.890
as an attendant to Crown Prince Li Ce.

33:35.580 --> 33:36.440
Your Highness!

33:39.270 --> 33:39.880
Your Highness!

33:39.880 --> 33:40.790
We found Miss Chun'er.

33:40.790 --> 33:41.640
Where did you find her?

33:41.640 --> 33:42.510
Did you have people bring her back?

33:42.510 --> 33:44.030
She came back on her own.

33:44.030 --> 33:45.880
She's in her room now.

34:03.640 --> 34:04.240
Chunxing.

34:04.750 --> 34:05.400
Come here.

34:16.090 --> 34:17.650
Is this Princess Fu?

34:17.960 --> 34:18.840
Princess Fu?

34:19.360 --> 34:19.880
Yes.

34:19.880 --> 34:22.540
She was close to our prince
when they were young.

34:23.280 --> 34:23.960
But...

34:24.280 --> 34:25.960
But later, she met with misfortune
along with Prince of Pingnan

34:25.960 --> 34:27.000
and was gone for many years.

34:27.000 --> 34:29.530
After returning,
she became distant from us.

34:32.590 --> 34:33.850
Is she in Tangjing now?

34:34.280 --> 34:34.880
Yes.

34:35.150 --> 34:36.880
I heard that since she came back,

34:36.880 --> 34:38.840
she has been staying
at the Crown Prince's Mansion.

34:38.840 --> 34:39.920
The Crown Prince likes her

34:39.920 --> 34:41.440
and wants to marry her.

34:41.800 --> 34:42.400
Chun'er!

34:49.190 --> 34:49.840
Chun'er,

34:50.400 --> 34:52.190
where have you been these past two days?

34:52.190 --> 34:53.650
I was so worried about you.

35:00.840 --> 35:01.510
Chun'er.

35:03.280 --> 35:04.610
Chun'er, what's wrong?

35:04.960 --> 35:06.280
Did something happen?

35:08.760 --> 35:09.880
You like me, right?

35:11.780 --> 35:14.450
Then marry me as your consort.

35:15.150 --> 35:17.150
I want to be Princess Consort of Luo.

35:33.590 --> 35:34.390
Your Majesty.

35:52.880 --> 35:53.810
General Shiyan.

35:55.280 --> 35:55.960
Here!

36:04.710 --> 36:06.040
Great Yan and Great Yong

36:06.230 --> 36:07.690
have been at war for years,

36:07.710 --> 36:09.370
and the people are exhausted.

36:09.590 --> 36:10.790
This journey of yours

36:10.930 --> 36:13.260
is to bring back Great Yan's lost generals

36:13.590 --> 36:14.720
and soldiers for me,

36:14.960 --> 36:16.760
end the war with Great Yong,

36:17.050 --> 36:19.110
and bring even a brief moment of peace

36:19.850 --> 36:21.710
to the countless people of Great Yan!

36:21.710 --> 36:22.770
Yes, Your Majesty!

36:28.230 --> 36:29.830
We will not fail our mission!

36:30.150 --> 36:31.550
We will not fail our mission!

36:31.550 --> 36:33.150
We will not fail our mission!

36:33.150 --> 36:36.000
We will not fail our mission!

36:38.790 --> 36:39.580
Lord Cheng.

36:40.320 --> 36:41.400
This is the list for the prisoners of war

36:41.400 --> 36:42.880
exchange between Great Yan and Great Yong,

36:42.880 --> 36:44.190
along with the compensation

36:44.190 --> 36:45.090
for the wounded.

36:45.090 --> 36:46.090
Please review it.

36:56.330 --> 36:58.470
[He Xiao]

37:23.960 --> 37:26.360
Since your presence here
is Her Majesty's goodwill,

37:26.360 --> 37:27.670
we will travel

37:27.670 --> 37:28.760
with you.

37:29.800 --> 37:30.470
Lord Zhan!

37:30.500 --> 37:31.500
Wait!

37:32.000 --> 37:32.960
Zhao Chun'er.

37:33.340 --> 37:35.880
Why are you claiming to be
the Princess Consort of Luo

37:35.880 --> 37:37.480
personally appointed by me?

37:40.510 --> 37:41.470
Chu Qiao,

37:41.960 --> 37:43.360
rest in peace.
